# TOC File Format

## Required Directives

```
## Interface: 120001
## Title: Addon Name
## Author: Author Name
## Version: 0.1.0
## SavedVariables: AddonNameDB
```

Interface version format: XXYYZZ (XX=expansion, YY=major, ZZ=minor). Current Retail: 120001.

## File Loading

Files load in exact order listed. Lua before XML. Libraries first, then core, then UI modules.

## Comments

Lines starting with `#` are comments. Use for section headers:

```
# Libraries
Libs\LibStub.lua

# Core
core\core.lua
```

## Dependencies

- `## Dependencies:` - hard requirement, addon fails without
- `## OptionalDeps:` - loads first if present, not required
